t a job. .. Then to boot, my entire network of friends and family discouraged me from taking the opportunity because they sympathized with my sisters plight. The poor girl is just trying to find her independence. How cruel am I to take that opportunity away from her.. My pride is sore. But I suppose this is the first step. isn&amp;#39;t it. &lt;br /&gt;Lovely story telling takes place in these comments. In any case,fine sir, you are changing lives with this blog. Thank you for the hope. &lt;br /&gt;A wise woman told me once that hope is the only thing we&amp;#39;re entitled to. Endless hope. &lt;br /&gt;Perhaps you would understand. </content><link rel='edit' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109831369489082264/comments/default/2893585688053836258'/><link rel='self' type='application/atom+xml' href='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/109831369489082264/comments/default/2893585688053836258'/><link rel='alternate' type='text/html' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/im-not-bum.html?showComment=1348445673875#c2893585688053836258' title=''/><author><name>Anonymous</name><email>noreply@blogger.com</email><gd:image rel='http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail' width='16' height='16' src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif'/></author><thr:in-reply-to xmlns:thr='http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0' href='http://guide2homelessness.blogspot.com/2004/10/im-not-bum.html' ref='tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-109831369489082264' source='http://www.blogger.com/feeds/8752543/posts/default/109831369489082264' type='text/html'/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.itemClass" value="pid-1825419222"/><gd:extendedProperty name="blogger.displayTime" value="5:14 PM"/></entry><entry><id>tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-8752543.post-3222742216465317698</id><published>2012-09-09T20:26:34.453-07:00</published><updated>2012-09-09T20:26:34.453-07:00</updated><title type='text'>Dear ModestMike - You&amp;#39;re NOT alone!!! I&amp;#39